Once a upon  a time there lived a monkey who recited jamun tree,which was on the banks of river.
in the same forest there lived a CROCODILE and its WIFE.....
one day a crocodile came to banks of river and waited under the tree.
the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits. the crocodile came came
 back next day for more fruits and he loved them . as days passed  on crocodile
  and monkey became good friends.
